Package: dverse
Title: Document a Universe of Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9004
Authors@R: 
    person("Mauro", "Lepore", , "maurolepore@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "ctr", "cre"))
Description: Creates a data frame of the metadata associated to the
    documentation of a collection of R packages. If you maintain universe
    meta-package, it helps you to easily create a universal reference for
    its website.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/maurolepore/dverse,
    https://maurolepore.github.io/dverse/
BugReports: https://github.com/maurolepore/dverse/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports: 
    cli,
    dplyr,
    glue,
    rlang,
    tibble,
    utils
Suggests: 
    DT,
    knitr,
    testthat,
    withr
Config/Needs/website: rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
